This product is going to help millions of people who are deaf they simply have to press a button 
on the product put it on any sound effect they like at it will recognize what sound effect it is. This product will only cost 150 AED.
Our goal is to just help the world with this product. People who have hearing problems will not ever be left out and will be treated the same way.
Our target audience is mainly for old people because statistics show that some people who are 60-70 years old. 
They start getting hearing problems and when they turn 80 years old they get hearing loss which is soon going to make them deaf.
